These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, singing, woodworking
House: victorian, farmhouse, art-deco, townhouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, motorbike, taxi
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
 6. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the townhouse house is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the person driving the taxi is the art-deco house##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the art-deco house is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person driving the motorbike##1
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping     | dancing   | woodworking | singing |
| House   | farmhouse | townhouse   | victorian   | art-deco  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| Transport     | airplane    | motorbike | jet-ski     | taxi    |

