.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, malaysian, turkish, indonesian
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the fan of salsa is between the owner of the dog and the fan of indie##2
 2. the malaysian is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the german is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the indonesian##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the owner of the frog##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the indonesian is on the left of the malaysian##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the german is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the german is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the indonesian is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Nationality      | german | turkish | indonesian  | malaysian  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | dog    | frog  |

