.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, old-henry, bongani, pall-mall
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, house, indie, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, german, italian
 1. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the italian##1
 2. the fonseca-smoker is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is the fan of house##1
 4. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
 5. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
 7. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the german##3
 9. the british is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the fan of indie is not the brazilian##6
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the italian is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
13. the fan of trance is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
14. the brazilian is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Cigar      | fonseca      | pall-mall  | bongani | old-henry        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | chess   | baking   | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | house   | indie    | dubstep      |
| Nationality   | british   | italian | german   | brazilian    |

