.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, swisher, oliveros, bluemaster
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, musician, police-officer
4 different pets are kept: goat, hedgehog, pony, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, subway, van
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
 2. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the electrician##8
 3. the owner of the goat is the montecristo-smoker##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 5. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
 6. the person driving the van is the swisher-smoker##1
 7. the police-officer is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 8. the musician is on the far right##1
 9. the electrician is not to the right of the oliveros-smoker##8
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
13. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the police-officer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Cigar    | swisher          | montecristo | oliveros        | bluemaster    |
| Job         | police-officer | doctor   | electrician | musician  |
| Pet         | pony           | goat     | snake       | hedgehog  |
| Transport   | van            | subway   | scooter     | quad-bike |

