.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, lemonade, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, puzzles, rock-climbing
4 different games are played: poker, scrabble, snooker, monopoly
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, roller, subway
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 2. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 5. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
 6. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 8. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the person playing snooker##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the person playing monopoly##7
11. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | lemonade        | fanta        | coffee        | water   |
| Hobby       | card-games      | camping      | rock-climbing | puzzles |
| Game         | monopoly | snooker | scrabble     | poker  |
| Transport   | roller          | jet-ski      | quad-bike     | subway  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, singing, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, social-worker, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, western
City: new-york, venice, liverpool, london
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the bartender##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##5
 4. the teacher is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the social-worker##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the person traveling to venice##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the social-worker##8
 8. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the social-worker and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | singing   | board-games   | collecting |
| Job           | bartender | doctor    | social-worker | teacher    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | adventure | animation     | western    |
| City   | new-york   | liverpool      | venice         | london     |

 